{"tid":1640311,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"未FC 謝sir已獲發「綠卡」","createTime":"2019-10-09T02:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T04:16:32.000Z","uid":114678,"like":43,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"27000b0bfb1e2059e65885df7f8d58b89276100f","tid":1640311,"uid":114678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EpLmaXH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEpLmaXH.jpg&h=89ae25f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n平安咭 又名綠卡 香港人力資源有限公司獲勞工處授權簽發「建造業安全訓練証明書」予成功完成課程之學員。<br />\n<br />\n謝振中 綠卡呀 !! 收野喇!!<br />\n<br />\n攞啦 柒頭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sixPjTv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsixPjTv.png&h=eef7cc14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"442b87fb32cc4e7555ab862a9868e71cd89d70e2","tid":1640311,"uid":312125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:13:08.000Z","msg":"（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a><br />\n<br />\n星期二（10月8日）早上，港鐵就宣布提前在晚上八點停駛，點解政府未卜先知出現動亂？其實政府有心製造一個長期嘅亂局，然後用緊急法立更多惡法，其中最近葉國謙就話要準備封網，呢樣嘢可以對香港抗爭造成極嚴重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>斷網可毒啞香港人，新疆前車可鑑</ins></span></strong><br />\n斷網真係落實嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\">最惡劣係好似新疆咁徹底斷網</span>，只有政府部門先可以上網，<span style=\"color: red;\">徹底封網的話，大家不但難以互通抗爭消息，而且香港訊息難以傳到海外，香港人也難以接收海外消息。西方人對香港嘅了解，只能經過政府嘅官方說法，或極少數流出嘅真相。</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">新疆早在2009年封網，同時限制境外人士到新疆旅遊，斷絕新疆對外聯繫，結果近年就出現新疆集中營。呢方面大家一定要警惕！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家不能掉以輕心</strong><br />\n或者有人認為政府會顧及香港嘅國際環境唔會輕易斷網，但現在中共已經失去理性，當中央黔驢技窮，損害香港利益而徹底封網並非不可。就好似半年前大家都唸唔到香港已經失去遊行以及戴口罩嘅自由。<br />\n<br />\n本文為節錄，全文請到此瀏覽：<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a>"},{"pid":"468d3a12cd51481b444e796ddf477e2176db0c32","tid":1640311,"uid":51641,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:14:25.000Z","msg":"好玩咩標題黨"},{"pid":"51864b8d38c7bb6882e04846732babd38990d6f5","tid":1640311,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:14:38.000Z","msg":"收啦收啦"},{"pid":"d265493e9ce94a7e9e7c530766158a972debba1b","tid":1640311,"uid":267277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:15:16.000Z","msg":"diu 嚇死人咩"},{"pid":"1554e96eb31caae16d25d5425095624555b4f17f","tid":1640311,"uid":281417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7003e135bcbedbb82f48f9176bd24b37873829e4","tid":1640311,"uid":124048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562143c1f5e0093508f4c701501c8db534558bb2","tid":1640311,"uid":283919,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:23:51.000Z","msg":"條頸比人擰左好多個圈"},{"pid":"a56a028ccdf810d8b9ffda2b3f4a9d5a9eb9af41","tid":1640311,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15500611454176ed0942e65991e71a54afed90b1","tid":1640311,"uid":287577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:46:43.000Z","msg":"Shit post, pull"},{"pid":"b496bb9b4d5d67a0423bb9ddeb9129af7560d499","tid":1640311,"uid":166506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:48:59.000Z","msg":"嚇親 <br />\n推 <img src=\"/assets/face